w'><dt>Next owner</dt><dd>Customer success manager</dd></div><div class='handoff-row'><dt>Action</dt><dd>Confirm procurement timeline and identify the new sponsor path.</dd></div><div class='handoff-row'><dt>Risk reason</dt><dd>Champion change with a 28 percent usage decline.</dd></div><div class='handoff-row'><dt>Evidence gap</dt><dd>Procurement dates before save plan or executive escalation.</dd></div></dl><div class='actions'><button class='button' type='button'>Record handoff</button><button class='button secondary' type='button'>Send to meeting</button></div></section></aside></section></main>"}
